{"tid":1604863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]如何令10.1抗爭針對「國殤」？","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:00:37.000Z","uid":234159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85e2d26c988c736f38249b3423bfd5766d934a40","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"由6月之今，香港的衝突場面已經好多，外媒的報導已令外國大部分地方覺得<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港混亂、警察濫暴</strong></span> 但同時要承認的是，暴力的畫面令人麻木。即使係想勇武，我地點樣令到10.1當日的畫面不一樣？<br />\n<br />\n我地要針對<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國殤，共產政權</strong></span>。我地要voice out的是希望香港有自治。我地需要創意，需要噱頭，需要多人，吸引國際的眼球，落中共面<br />\n<br />\n9.29，本來係anti chinazi，對抗極權。大家覺得目的突唔突出？我覺得似爭取番五大訴求，屌番popo。我認同要做，但主要口號要係同番中共/極權有關。之前有人話預演新疆集中營，我覺得方向正確，會唔會可地區戰前做？雖然你可以話popo咁執法就係極權，但未夠強去控訴政權本身<br />\n<br />\n仲有一日！不如諗下有咩口號落到中共面，突出到香港想要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自治、民主</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d20e4473020d31f0be4a54425dfa4817edb88105","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"重post"},{"pid":"477169b8134c326279fa12af5ff1996dc84dba6a","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"958dd2e4a6f20638ee0f12349688333b09b1cd05","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffdba881e9efe915f77da633fb4b913dcea205f2","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7208e2b0c9ec0a4d9b6403d5e119ffd9e615979a","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44ab9aa32a339b5c97a1774a4f5bea86fa67b9dd","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"142d2a0c41cd67f4884e5b6d33eb15d06f84a1b8","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed287a92e8d80fee7e591b5f117bbd592e8c8e6d","tid":1604863,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c130201515aec1f5d37ad46807699115524e619","tid":1604863,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"[N區開花] 唔攻狗必救，係做唔到分散狗力效果，狗只會處理完必救先TG炸走你<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nhttps://li<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div><a href=\"http://h.kg/1604810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fh.kg%2F1604810&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=2c4130f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h.kg/1604810</a>"},{"pid":"f6c977f7a3f177313edf6b7664e14b048ba24cd7","tid":1604863,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"今晚需要一個集氣大會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604777</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1c8e9850c31d63c2c5e01c1b695cf1986a514e5","tid":1604863,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"記住攻共黨為上，狗隻為下"}]}